: 1520953252:0;Thanks for the update.
: 1520953252:0;The reason why they user still appears in the customer list is due to the current *Customer permissions* assigned to this project. Your [permissions|https://tenengroup.atlassian.net/servicedesk/admin/IS/customer-permissions\] are set to _Anyone with an account on the site_, therefore, any Jira user will always have access to this project. 
